CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: TON Strategy Company (Nasdaq: TONX) is focused on the accumulation of Toncoin ($TON) for long-term investment, whether acquired through deployment of proceeds from capital raising transactions, staking rewards or via open market purchases. The Company aims to steadily expand its $TON treasury, stake $TON and to support the development of a tokenized economy inside Telegram's billion-user platform.
